    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因交易商关注美国库存和中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国行业组织暗示全国原油库存将增加，且拜登政府再次努力确保中东停火，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法瓦罗支持巴西加入“一带一路”倡议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/favaro-favors-brazil-joining-china-s-belt-road-initiative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农业和畜牧业部长卡洛斯·法瓦罗在圣保罗 B20 峰会的彭博新经济论坛上表示，必须扩大贸易伙伴范围，以应对保护主义措施。（葡萄牙语，附英语翻译。）]]></description>
